Executive Profile
Michael L. Glazer  Chief Executive Officer, President and Director, Stage Stores, Inc.AgeTotal Calculated CompensationThis person is connected to 1 Board Members in 1 different organizations across 4 different industries.See Board Relationships68$3,633,290As of Fiscal Year 2016
Background

		Mr. Michael L. Glazer has been the Chief Executive Officer and President of Stage Stores Inc. since April 19, 2012. Mr. Glazer served as the Interim President and Interim Chief Executive Officer of Stage Stores Inc. from March 28, 2012 to April 19, 2012. He served as the President and Chief Executive Officer at Mattress Giant Corporation. He has been the Chief Executive Officer at K B Toy Of Mississippi, Inc., K B Toy Of Michigan, Inc., K B Toy Of New York, Inc., K B ... Toy Of Missouri Inc. and K B Toy Of Minnesota, Inc. He served as Vice President of K B Toy Of Kansas, Inc. He served as Managing Director of K B Toy Of Puerto Rico, Inc. Mr. Glazer previously served as the Managing Director at Team Neu since August 2005. He served as the Medical Director of K B Toys Of Puerto Rico, Inc. He served as Senior Vice President of Outsourcing Services Business Unit and General Manager of Outsourcing Services Business Unit at K B Toy Of Utah, Inc. He served as an Executive Vice President and General Merchandise Manager at Kb Toy Of New Jersey, Inc. Mr. Glazer served as the Chief Financial Officer and Vice President at K B Toy Of Oklahoma, Inc. He served as Vice President of Human Resources at K B Toy Of Iowa, Inc. He served as President of Community and External Affairs Division's Southwest at K B Toy Of Illinois, Inc. He served as Senior Vice President of K B Toy Of Delaware, Inc. Mr. Glazer served as an Executive Vice President - Wireless Business Unit at Kb Toy Of Massachusetts, Inc. He served as Vice President and General Manager of Automotive Components at K B Toy Of Washington, Inc. He served as an Executive Vice President of Worldwide Sales and Professional Services at K B Toy Of Texas, Inc. Mr. Glazer served as the Chief Technology Officer and Vice President for Platforms and Solutions - Infospaces Wireless Business at K B Toy Of Hawaii, Inc. He served as President of Piercing Pagoda® and Senior Vice President at K B Toy Of Louisiana, Inc. He served as the Chairman and Chief Executive Officer - Bear Stearns Asset Management (BSAM) at K B Toy Of California, Inc. Mr. Glazer served as the Chief Executive Officer of The Parent Company. He served as the President and Chief Executive Officer of KB Toys, Inc. from May 1996 to August 2005. From May 1995 to May 1996, he served as the President at Big Lots Stores Inc. and from September 1990 to January 1995, he served as President of The Bombay Company Inc. He served as a Director of CPI Corp. from November 2008 to August 22, 2012. Mr. Glazer served as the Chairman of the Board of K B Toy Of Pennsylvania, Inc. He served as a Vice Chairman of K B Toy Of Kentucky, Inc. He has been a Director of Stage Stores Inc. since March 29, 2012 and previously served as its Independent Director since August 24, 2001. He served as a Director of Cantab at K B Toy Of Puerto Rico, Inc. He served as a Director - TransWestern Communications Company Inc. - General Partner of K B Toy Of New Hampshire, Inc. Mr. Glazer served as a Director of K B Toys Of Puerto Rico and also as a Director of Cantab. He served as Director of Bear Stearns Asset Management (BSAM) at K B Toy Of California, Inc. He served as a Director of K B Toy Of Georgia, Inc., K B Toy Of Delaware, Inc., K B Toy Of New Mexico, Inc., K B Toy Of West Virginia Inc., K B Toy Of Rhode Island, Inc., K B Toy Of South Carolina Inc., K B Toy Of Wisconsin, Inc., K B Toy Of Connecticut, Inc., K B Toy Of Indiana, Inc., K B Toy Of North Carolina, Inc. and K B Toy Of Virginia, Inc. He served as a Director of KB Toys Inc. since August 24, 2001; Big Lots Inc. until May 20, 2003; Brookstone Inc. since June 1996 and K B Toy Of Maryland, Inc. Mr.Glazer received a B.A. from the University of California Berkley and an MBA from Columbia University.Read Full Background




