Insider Activity


Individual




Michael L. Glazer



Mr. Michael L. Glazer is on the Board of Directors at Stage Stores, Inc. Mr. Glazer was previously employed as President & Chief Executive Officer by Mattress Giant Corp., an Independent Director by CPI Corp., a Managing Director by Team Neu, President & Chief Executive Officer by KB Toys, Inc., and President by Bombay & Co., Inc. He also served on the board at Brookstone, Inc. and Big Lots, Inc. He received his undergraduate degree from the University of California, Berkeley and an MBA from Columbia University.



