Michael L. Glazer - President, Chief Executive Officer & Director
I'm not going to say the specific number to you other than to say that you know our expectations and we're certainly focused on top line and there were just an awful lot of things that happened in the first quarter. I mean the good news is it was first quarter and we got the rest of the year ahead of us and as we said for Mother's Day, we feel it was just – I can't tell you how spectacular that week was. I mean, you obviously see how much it moved the needle for us and it'd created some nice momentum and so we'll see how the rest of the year plays out, but, yes, it was disappointing in the first quarter on the top line basis.
Charles P. Grom - Sterne Agee CRT
