I will say that a lot of people have revealed what their first quarter comps are, and you know it was not an easy quarter for a lot of people out there. You did see as we got to the tail end of the quarter, people being a little more aggressive, extending events or adding events in to try to move their comp as we got closer to the end of the quarter. But I would say for the most part around the peaks, it has been competitive and will always be competitive.
